description._content: Piazza del Duomo, [Milan, Italy] [between ca. 1890 and ca. 1900]. 1 photomechanical print : photochrom, color. Notes: Print shows the Piazza del Duomo (Cathedral Square) and the Milan Cathedral. (Source: Flickr Commons project, 2009) Title from item.
